<h2 class="page-header" id="profile-image-intro">Profile Images</h2>
<p class="lead">Provides a contextually-centered image, adjusted to completely cover a congruent area (square or circle).</p>
<h3 id="profile-basic-example">Basic Example</h3>
<div class="bs-example">
    {{profile-image imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image blurred="true" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
</div>
<div class="highlight">
<pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="cm">/* Basic implementation yields a square, small profile image */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>
<span class="cm">/* adding 'blurred="true"' to the options converts to a pixelated base */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="na">blurred=</span><span class="s">"true"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span></code></pre>
</div>
<h3 id="profile-image-sizes">Size Variations</h3>
<p>In addition to the standard (small) implementation, size can be specified by adding the <code>size="*"</code> modifier.</p>
<div class="bs-example" id="profile-basic-example">
    {{profile-image size="small" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image size="medium" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image size="large" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image size="xlarge" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}<br/>

    {{profile-image blurred="true" size="small" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image blurred="true" size="medium" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image blurred="true" size="large" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image blurred="true" size="xlarge" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
</div>
<div class="highlight">
<pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="cm">/* Size variations are set as properties in the component options */</span>
<span class="cm">/* size="small" */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">size=</span><span class="s">"small"</span> <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>
<span class="cm">/* size="medium" */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">size=</span><span class="s">"medium"</span> <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>
<span class="cm">/* size="large" */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">size=</span><span class="s">"large"</span> <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>
<span class="cm">/* size="xlarge" */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">size=</span><span class="s">"xlarge"</span> <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span></code></pre>
</div>
<h3 id="profile-image-shapes">Shape Variations</h3>
<p>Profile Images also come in both squre or circle shape by adding the <code>shape="*"</code> option.</p>
<div class="bs-example" id="profile-shape-example">
    {{profile-image shape="square" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
    {{profile-image shape="circle" imageSrc='/img/profiles/emmet.jpg'}}
</div>
<div class="highlight">
<pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="cm">/* Shape is set as a property, with square as default */</span>
<span class="cm">/* shape="square" :: default */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span>
<span class="cm">/* shape="circle" */</span>
<span class="nt">&lbrace;&lbrace;</span>profile-image <span class="na">shape=</span><span class="s">"circle"</span> <span class="na">imageSrc=</span><span class="s">"/img/profiles/emmet.jpg"</span> <span class="nt">&rbrace;&rbrace;</span></code></pre>
</div>
